1.pT: Gendai ni okeru shikaku wo chûshin to shita bunka no kenkyû

2.pT: Shôhi to yûkyô ni yoru gendai sei shônen no hikaku bunrui

3.pT: Chiiki bunna shinkô no mondai ten to sono kôseki

6.pT: Sabu karuchâ wo meguru tasha to no kankeiron

7.pT: Taijin kankei ni okeru kôdô sentaku no tokuchô

8.pT: Ryôsan gata seizô katei ni okeru hikaku kenkyu

9.pT: Tokushu heisa jôkyô ka ni okeru setsumei gimu no yûmu ni tsuite

10.pT: Keizai kôka kara kangaeru yoka shôhi no fechishizumu

11.pT: Toshi gata hanzai ni okeru akui no shozai ron

12.pT: Soshiki no sai kôchiku ji ni hassei suru kadai to taisaku
